    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Pick the dill fronds. Chop the cucumber and thinly slice the red onion. Dice or tear the smoked salmon into bite-sized chunks. Add everything to another bowl with the juice of a lemon, then stir the sesame seeds through and add a drizzle of olive oil. Toss together with the capers."
    },
    {
